# React Component Patterns

## Structure

- Functional components only. No class components.
- Export named functions: `export function DashboardPage() {}`
- Keep components in `src/modules/<feature>/` for page-level components.
- Shared components go in `src/components/`.

## Data Loading

Services are async. Use `useState` + `useEffect` for loading:

```typescript
const [data, setData] = useState<MyType[]>([])
useEffect(() => {
  myService.getData().then(setData)
}, [dependency])
```

## Hooks

- `useAuth()` - Current user, login/logout.
- `useDataSegregation()` - `getAccessibleStations()`, `canAccessStation(name)`, `userUnit`.
- `usePermissions()` - `canEdit`, `canManageUsers`, `isReadOnly`.

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS classes directly on elements.
- Brand colors: `bg-[#1a3d47]`, `text-[#2C5F6F]`.
- Cards: `bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4`.
- Tables: `<thead className="bg-[#1a3d47] text-white">`.

## Notifications

```typescript
import { toast } from 'sonner'
toast.success('Operacao realizada')
toast.error('Erro ao processar')
```
